{"tid":281021,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得倉鼠好嘔心","createTime":"2017-06-12T12:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T14:42:57.000Z","uid":58391,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf12afecefd58141a65163dab5cd8e95166ad7b6","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"佢地既外表同老鼠無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為有少少顏色就覺得你好q咩？<br />\n你只係一隻唔係黑色既老鼠咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁細粒攬又唔係 一陣太大力又怕整死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望定定望住你果個樣真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係見到都唔開胃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慎入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_SoahbnYwRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_SoahbnYwRk&d=uxwN5JqRpwkDwaH%2Br6EYGsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=281d9f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_SoahbnYwRk</a>"},{"pid":"2f38dd01fa9a9cd40b72fddfccb369dcfc00297a","tid":281021,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"老鼠唔得意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d373962ff7c73c9908a3098db1d2ae1e2b6940e8","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老鼠唔得意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔得意 仲好恐怖"},{"pid":"294338dcf50fd9cfbe5e966e732af086fc863067","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24af41f38916faef6