 /> <br />\n但垃圾鼠唔同 咁柒仲喺個玻璃櫃度show出黎獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe609102d7a9ad6df302682bfd4cb71c8994ca3","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老鼠=loser,毒撚<br />\n倉鼠=人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無撚分別 都係肉撚酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26becc6f31d53d289f8b7a73290ba6b2f32c70ae","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條片似係個細路嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻倉鼠食哂d bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔夜飯都嘔埋出黎"},{"pid":"41a9585f55fbb99b48524d2399eecb99e9fbf3cb","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坑渠老鼠勁得意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唯一一次 我返大家樂 有隻老鼠食左老鼠藥 <br />\n之後訓咗喺度奄奄一息 個刻最得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c9d8bb580a174f3332b261e03ed8c70acf805f","tid":281021,"uid":13033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5947ccb6b9a51027f63c4b2c5da37229ee4bd06","tid":281021,"uid":121245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得老鼠好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺街見到啲屍體會走去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2bac58d8d36f1cc55f5e0e6f78c59a6ed2b20b","tid":281021,"uid":109607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"朋友最多轉圈轉圈哈姆共你"},{"pid":"d9b77e7fd5c347c68dbb93d4336