"pid":"dca31e92c60bf28d45d0336be56b7962fd1218a4","tid":281021,"uid":58391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得老鼠好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺街見到啲屍體會走去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死左就最可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}